55.4	The_Departed	The Departed	The Departed is a 2006 American crime thriller film directed by Martin Scorsese. The screenplay by William Monahan was based on the 2002 Hong Kong film Infernal Affairs. The film stars Leonardo DiCaprio, Matt Damon, Jack Nicholson, Mark Wahlberg, Martin Sheen, Ray Winstone, Vera Farmiga, Anthony Anderson and Alec Baldwin.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/50/Departed234.jpg/220px-Departed234.jpg
